===Twin towns – sister cities===
Dili is twinned with the following places:

* Canberra, Australia (2004)
* Coimbra, Portugal (2002)
* Darwin, Australia (2003)
* Lisbon, Portugal (2001)
* Macau, China (2024)
* Manila, Philippines (2011)
* Margao, India (2001)
* Okinawa, Japan (2005)
* Praia, Cape Verde (2001)
